    "description": "Cafe Coffee Day is actively seeking a talented and motivated Floor Manager to join our dynamic team in Ahmedabad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Cafe Coffee Day:\nCafe Coffee Day is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure visual merchandising standards are maintained at all times\n• Monitor inventory levels and coordinate replenishment activities\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in Planogram\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Cafe Coffee Day!",
